This event will involve a lot of bot commands and exploration. Use bot commands to explore your surroundings, and find small quests for rewards. You can explore an area, look at objects, or interact with objects using the command for the area. ex: <pf> is the command for the petrified forest area, and if you wish to look at a gnarled tree, you'd type <!pf gnarled tree> to do so. Actions to take or things to look at will most often required one-three words, and will never require more than four words. If you discover a quest, do a short rp relating to that quest. You are free to rp ANY of the involved npcs to facilitate this.

It's been sometime since she's stepped foot into the desert sands and made her way here... but it was as hot as always! The first order of things that she does is buy herself new attire! But he's not truly scared until Owein starts asking questions—surely a guard—vassal—whatever, someone who's used to fighting—surely he's seen stab wounds before, knows what they look like—and then Albert talking about unbranding him—not even just a regular scar— "Wha—whazgoinnon—" He tries to look, heart pounding in his chest—he only barely lifts his head up before he can't move further, a wave of pain radiating from his side. His jaw clenches, eyes squeezing shut, throat tightening. His hands clench, too, wanting comfort—and then further, nails digging into skin, as it starts itching unbearably. It's—it's working. It's healing. He knows. But it's awful. Seconds, minutes, he doesn't know how long, but it feels like forever until the feeling finally fades, bringing with it some measure of relief. "What's.... what's wrong with it?" (edited)
